import { IonCard, IonCardContent, IonCardHeader, IonCardTitle, IonItem, IonLabel, IonList } from "@ionic/react"
import Layout from "../../components/Layout/Layout"
import data_app from '../../assets/data_app.json';

const Home: React.FC = () => { 
    
    return <Layout name='Inicio' > 
        <IonCard>
            <IonCardHeader>
                <IonCardTitle>{data_app.title}</IonCardTitle>
            </IonCardHeader>
            <IonCardContent>
                <IonLabel>
                    { data_app.description}
                </IonLabel>
                <IonList>
                    {data_app.data_access.map((value: any, index: number) =>
                        <IonItem key={index}>
                        <IonLabel>{value.name}</IonLabel>
                        </IonItem>
                    )}
                </IonList>
            </IonCardContent>
        </IonCard>
    </Layout>
} 

export default Home;
